explanation: This dataset has managed access restrictions. Users must request access and have their request approved by the dataset's Access Requirement Team (ACT) or designated reviewers before they can download or access the data.
This dataset has no access restrictions. It is publicly accessible and can be downloaded by any registered Synapse user.
This dataset has controlled access restrictions requiring data use certification. Users must complete a data use certification process and agree to specific terms of use before accessing the data.
This dataset requires managed access approval. Users need to submit an access request including information about their intended use, which will be reviewed by the access requirement administrators.
This is an open access dataset with no restrictions. Any authenticated Synapse user can freely access and download the data.
